OL,4,Cwho died spared jail
OL,6,FA care home worker who mistakenly gave
OL,7,Fthe wrong medication to a patient who
OL,8,Flater died has been spared jail.
OL,10,FJane Barnard, 67, gave Derek Davies,
OL,11,F75, medication prescribed to another
OL,12,Fresident at the Wheatridge Court care
OL,13,Fhome which employed her in Gloucester.
OL,15,FMs Barnard denied killing Mr Davies
OL,16,Fand, following a trial at Gloucester
OL,17,FCrown Court, a jury found her not
OL,18,Fguilty of manslaughter.
