OL,4,Cwho died spared jail
OL,6,FShe was spared a custodial sentence
OL,7,Fand ordered to carry out 100 hours of
OL,8,Funpaid work.
OL,10,FMr Davies died on 8 September 2021
OL,11,Fafter Ms Barnard mistakenly gave him
OL,12,Fmedication prescribed for fellow
OL,13,Fpatient Jason Dodsworth, which
OL,14,Fincluded 90mg of slow-release morphine.
OL,16,FShe previously pleaded guilty to one
OL,17,Fcount of wilful neglect, having failed
OL,18,Fto disclose she had wrongfully
OL,19,Fadministered the morphine.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
