OL,6,FThe trial heard the morphine, a
OL,7,Fcontrolled drug, had been stored in
OL,8,Fthe wrong place when it was retrieved
OL,9,Fby Barnard.
OL,11,FThe controlled drugs at the care home
OL,12,Fwere meant to be locked away in a
OL,13,Fdesignated room, and only administered
OL,14,Fwith two members of staff present.
OL,16,FHowever, Mr Dodsworth's morphine had
OL,17,Fbeen incorrectly stored in his
OL,18,Fbathroom cabinet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
