OL,6,FWhile Barnard was not involved in
OL,7,Fstoring the medication, the court
OL,8,Fheard she had failed to make the
OL,9,Fcorrect checks and follow procedure
OL,10,Fbefore administering the controlled
OL,11,Fdrug.
OL,13,FCrucially, she also took the drugs to
OL,14,Fthe wrong resident, Mr Davies, who had
OL,15,Fbeen sitting in a communal area of the
OL,16,Fhome on the morning of 6 September
OL,17,F2021.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
