OL,6,FAfter realising her mistake, she
OL,7,Fdisposed of the drugs Mr Davies should
OL,8,Fhave received and pretended the
OL,9,Fmedication she did give him had been
OL,10,Fdropped down the sink.
OL,12,FBarnard said she was in a "state" and
OL,13,Fcould not bring herself to tell
OL,14,Fcolleagues or medical professionals
OL,15,Fwhat she had done, even after Mr
OL,16,FDavies fell ill and was taken to
OL,17,Fhospital.
