OL,4,Cwho died spared jail
OL,6,FOn 8 September 2021, two days after
OL,7,Fthe incident, Barnard rang Kim Jones,
OL,8,Fdeputy manager of the home, to tell
OL,9,Fher she had given Mr Davies the wrong
OL,10,Fmedication.
OL,12,FWhen the care home contacted the
OL,13,Fhospital, it was confirmed Mr Davies
OL,14,Fhad died that morning.
OL,16,FThe original cause of death was
OL,17,Fdocumented as a brainstem stroke, but
OL,18,Fit was later understood Mr Davies'
OL,19,Factual cause of death was a
OL,20,Fconsequence of morphine toxicity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
