OL,6,FMr Justice Butcher said: "You
OL,7,Fcontinued to fail to mention the
OL,8,Fmistake you had made and which you
OL,9,Fknew was a serious one.
OL,11,F"It went further than simply not
OL,12,Fsaying anything. I accept, however,
OL,13,Fthat you did not intend to harm Mr
OL,14,FDavies."
