OL,6,FIn a statement issued by
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police at the end of
OL,8,Fthe trial, Mr Davies' family said:
OL,9,F"The last four years since our dad's
OL,10,Fdeath have been extremely upsetting
OL,11,Ffor our family, both because we have
OL,12,Fmissed him terribly and because we
OL,13,Fhave had to live without knowing what
OL,14,Fcaused his death and how it occurred.
OL,16,F"We have been kept in the dark, and
OL,17,Fthe uncertainty and lack of knowledge
OL,18,Fsurrounding the facts of his death
OL,19,Fhave left us in a permanent state of
OL,20,Ftorment, wondering what happened and
OL,21,Fhow much he might have suffered.
OL,26,@qD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
