OL,3,CCarer who gave wrong drugs to resident
OL,4,Cwho died spared jail
OL,6,F"This has affected the way we remember
OL,7,Fdad and his life, as well as our
OL,8,Fability to grieve, which has all been
OL,9,Fclouded by the criminal investigation.
OL,11,F"Going through this has been traumatic
OL,12,Ffor everyone involved ` our dad and
OL,13,Ffamily, as well as the defendant and
OL,14,Fher family ` there are no winners here.
OL,16,F"We don't know how much more time we
OL,17,Fwould have had with our dad, but these
OL,18,Fevents robbed us of that precious time
OL,19,Fand he is greatly missed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
